'''甜胶大戟'''（{{lang-xm|Euphorbia balsamifera}}；{{lang-es|tabaiba dulce}}）是[[大戟科|大戟科]][[大戟属|大戟属]]的一种[[木本植物|木本植物]]，分布于[[加那利群岛|加那利群岛]]、[[撒哈拉沙漠|撒哈拉沙漠]]、[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半岛]]等地。<ref>{{Cite web|title=''Euphorbia balsamifera'' Aiton|url=http://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:345730-1|accessdate=2021-03-26|work=Plants of the World Online|publisher=Kew Science|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707141346/http://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:345730-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>与其它大戟属植物不同，甜胶大戟的[[乳胶|乳汁]]微甜而没有苦辛味，凝固成胶状后可以食用或当做[[口香糖|口香糖]]。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DOtN2FjdRP0C&pg=PA758|publisher=Longman, Orme, Brown, Green and Longmans|first=Jonathan|last=Pereira|title=The Elements of Materia Medica, Part II|year=1840|location=London, England|pages=758|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706094934/https://books.google.com/books?id=DOtN2FjdRP0C&pg=PA758|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aIlhAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA192|publisher=Hippolyte Baillière|first=Matthias Jacob|last=Schleiden|title=The Plant; a Biography|year=1848|location=London, England|pages=192|others=Translated by Henfrey, Arthur|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706093509/https://books.google.com/books?id=aIlhAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA192|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=More than one sweet tabaiba: Disentangling the systematics of the succulent dendroid shrub ''Euphorbia balsamifera''|author=|url=https://pericles.pericles-prod.literatumonline.com/doi/abs/10.1111/jse.12656|last=Riina|first=Ricarda|last2=Villaverde|first2=Tamara|journal=Journal of Systematics and Evolution|issue=n/a|doi=10.1111/jse.12656|volume=n/a|language=en|issn=1759-6831|last3=Rincón‐Barrado|first3=Mario|last4=Molero|first4=Julià|last5=Sanmartín|first5=Isabel}}</ref>某些地区亦食用其叶片。<ref>{{Cite web|title=''Euphorbia balsamifera''|url=https://www.purdue.edu/hla/sites/famine-foods/famine_food/euphorbia-balsamifera/|accessdate=2021-03-26|work=Famine Foods|publisher=Purdue University|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706093604/https://www.purdue.edu/hla/sites/famine-foods/famine_food/euphorbia-balsamifera/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但甜胶大戟可能会造成[[贫血|贫血]]等副作用，不可多食。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Toxic effects of some plants in the genus ''Euphorbia'' on haematological and biochemical parameters of rats|author=|url=https://hrcak.srce.hr/67755|last=Adedapo|first=Adeolu A.|last2=Abatan|first2=Matthew O.|date=2004-02-21|journal=Veterinarski arhiv|issue=1|volume=74|pages=53–62|issn=0372-5480|last3=Olorunsogo|first3=Olufunso O.|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720233136/https://hrcak.srce.hr/67755|dead-url=no}}</ref>

